    "name": "World Guesser",
    "steam_appid": 2402620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402620/extras/7f8e8028f3ddd449e32cd814a27e782c.avif?t=1770432866\" width=618 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备开启一场横跨全球的飞机之旅！与其他选手同台竞技，参与大逃杀风格的地理挑战：将包裹依次送达指定目标国家，就是通往胜利的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402620/extras/9ca8bd0871a53a267c6a8b8cc0dbafc1.avif?t=1770432866\" width=618 height=77 /></span>但这还不止！在飞行途中释放你的专属能力，取得战略优势。启动涡轮加速甩开对手，或利用“透明”能力更清晰地掌握周围环境。有了这些工具，你就能像真正的王牌一样在天空中穿梭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402620/extras/d64d16c9dd9df28261187c8ab0b5d982.avif?t=1770432866\" width=618 height=77 /></span>当竞争愈发激烈，只有最娴熟、最具策略的玩家才能成为最后的胜者。准备迎接一场与时间赛跑的刺激对决——精准、速度与敏捷思考将是你最强的盟友。起飞、反超、夺冠，在 World Guess 中凯旋而归！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
